WEBVTT

00:02.360 --> 00:03.880
Recall the troops and return to court

00:04.920 --> 00:05.280
Yes

00:24.040 --> 00:24.760
Not long after

00:25.360 --> 00:27.880
Nandu City fell

00:55.080 --> 00:55.840
You're still here

00:57.360 --> 00:58.120
I've always been here

01:02.400 --> 01:03.440
No matter what the outcome

01:05.560 --> 01:07.840
I will face it together with Your Majesty

01:11.400 --> 01:14.080
Great Xuan's accumulation over decades

01:15.600 --> 01:17.080
Now destroyed in one fire

01:18.400 --> 01:20.240
It is my fault

01:22.920 --> 01:24.840
Since ancient times, rulers die with their state

01:26.280 --> 01:27.360
As long as I am here

01:29.840 --> 01:31.840
Great Xuan will not be humiliated

01:37.320 --> 01:38.280
Your Majesty still has a sword

01:41.160 --> 01:42.120
Has heroic spirit

01:43.360 --> 01:44.080
And me

01:47.640 --> 01:50.880
They say Chen and Sikong rule the realm together

01:52.400 --> 01:52.920
Now

01:55.000 --> 01:56.080
It is Chen and Sikong

01:58.080 --> 01:59.240
Facing survival and destruction together

02:03.520 --> 02:04.560
Arm me

02:06.320 --> 02:06.800
Yes

02:08.240 --> 02:08.760
Miss Chen

02:09.440 --> 02:10.160
What a coincidence

02:10.680 --> 02:11.840
I am here on my granduncle's orders

02:12.080 --> 02:13.600
To report to His Majesty

02:20.880 --> 02:23.360
Aren't my benefits a bit lacking?

02:24.040 --> 02:25.360
A mutually beneficial matter

02:25.680 --> 02:26.800
What else does Your Highness want?

02:27.360 --> 02:28.360
My friendship

02:29.760 --> 02:30.840
Does Your Highness dare to want it?

02:35.680 --> 02:37.040
You traitor

02:39.400 --> 02:40.600
Look at our ancestors

02:41.000 --> 02:41.920
Think about what you've done

02:44.040 --> 02:45.640
Do you still know your surname?

02:46.560 --> 02:47.320
Chen

02:49.840 --> 02:50.640
This is for Your Highness

02:51.440 --> 02:52.080
For the Chen family

02:52.840 --> 02:53.680
And for the realm

02:54.520 --> 02:55.520
The best outcome

03:10.600 --> 03:11.400
Are you afraid?

03:12.880 --> 03:13.800
With Your Majesty here

03:15.280 --> 03:15.680
I'm not afraid

03:22.080 --> 03:23.320
Beat the drums for me

03:24.240 --> 03:25.760
I will protect Great Xuan

03:26.560 --> 03:28.080
Until the end

03:34.080 --> 03:35.440
Corpses fill the palace

03:35.560 --> 03:37.000
Blood fills the streets

03:37.440 --> 03:40.320
This is the integrity Xuan Kingdom lacked for decades

03:41.080 --> 03:42.560
The capital's sun

03:43.640 --> 03:44.520
Has set
